<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-07-11T18:58:27-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-07-11T18:58:27-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-11T18:58:27-04:00</updated><title>以人工智能为重点的《复制法案》将使删除数字水印成为非法</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;一位手上有太多手指的法官用木槌的数字照片拼贴。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/hoz7lodN4C8X92q5fXZBsqF7aF4=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73456277/STK470_AI_LAW_CVIRGINIA_C.0 .jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图由 Cath Virginia / The Verge 绘制 |照片来自 Getty Images&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;Wm7vJX&quot;>;两党参议员小组&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.commerce.senate.gov/2024/7/cantwell-blackburn- heinrich-introduce-legislation-to-combat-ai-deepfakes-put-journalists-artists-songwriters-back-in-control-of-their-content&quot;>;引入了一项新法案&lt;/a>;，以使其更容易进行身份验证和检测人工智能生成的内容，并保护记者和艺术家的作品不被未经许可的人工智能模型吞噬。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;euhsgC&quot;>;《编辑和深造媒体内容来源保护和完整性法案》&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.documentcloud.org/documents/24804105-copied-act?responsive=1&amp;amp;title=1&quot;>;（COPIED Act）&lt;/a>; 将指导美国国家标准与技术研究院 (NIST)创建标准和指南，帮助证明内容的来源并检测合成内容，例如通过水印。它还指示该机构制定安全措施以防止篡改，并要求针对创意或新闻内容的人工智能工具允许用户附加有关其来源的信息并禁止...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:/ /www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196769/copied-act-cantwell-blackburn-heinrich-ai-journalists-artists&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196769/copied-act-cantwell-blackburn-heinrich-ai-journalists-artists" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196769/copied-act-cantwell-blackburn-heinrich-ai-journalists-artists</id><author><name>劳伦·费纳</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-11T18:16:35-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-11T18:16:35-04:00</updated><title>以下是 OpenAI 将如何确定其人工智能系统的强大程度</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;薄荷绿和黑色的 ChatGPT 徽标。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ZqwBhj9aWQiLaWOvzMmq4yfGM9c=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73456227/STK149_AI_02.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;jY88bn&quot;>;OpenAI 创建了一个内部规模来跟踪其大型语言模型在通用人工智能（或类人人工智能）方面取得的进展情报部门发言人&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-11/openai-sets-levels-to-track-progress-toward-superintelligent-ai&quot;>;告诉&lt; em>;Bloomberg&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;mCldqZ&quot;>;当今的聊天机器人，如 ChatGPT，处于 1 级。OpenAI 声称它已接近 2 级，定义为可以解决问题的系统博士水平的基本问题。 3 级是指能够代表用户采取行动的人工智能代理。第四级涉及可以创造新创新的人工智能。第 5 级是实现 AGI 的最后一步，人工智能可以执行整个人类组织的工作。 OpenAI 此前将 AGI 定义为“在最具经济价值的任务中超越人类的高度自治系统”。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;1PMpyv&quot;>;OpenAI 的...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196746/heres-how- openai-will-确定-how-powerful-its-ai-systems-are&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196746/heres-how-openai-will-determine-how-powerful-its-ai-systems-are" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196746/heres-how-openai-will-define-how-powerful-its-ai-systems-are</id><author><name>凯莉罗宾逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-11T17:53:20-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-11T17:53:20-04:00</updated><title> 《过山车之星》的滑滑续作让你建造自己的水上乐园</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;《过山车之星 2》截图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/XCSHId6Ct-JyoEzoG0w7OtzRKsY=/150x0:1770x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com /uploads/chorus_image/image/73456181/planet_coaster_2.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：前沿发展&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;2ZkdIs&quot;>;&lt;em>;过山车星球&lt;/em>;&#39;续集不再只是关于建造最好的主题公园：它也与水上公园有关。续集&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.frontier.co.uk/news/press-releases/ride-wave-much-anticipated-planet-coaster-2&quot;>;将于今年秋天推出&lt;/a>;，最后，您可以建造一切，从波浪池、漂流河到定制水滑梯。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;m3s7x1&quot;>;您还可以为您的水上体验配备更衣室、日光浴床、救生员等。 &lt;em>;Planet Coaster 2&lt;/em>; 在其前身的基础上添加了新的建筑和路径工具，以及先进的事件排序系统，可以为您的客人带来新的体验。还有新的游乐设施、风景作品和主题。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;GbMXj1&quot;>;《过山车之星 2》的另一个巧妙功能是能够与朋友创建共享主题公园 —但你们不能同时在公园里建造。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://store.steampowered.com/app/2688950/Planet_Coaster_2/&quot;>;T...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge .com/2024/7/11/24196770/planet-coaster-2-water-park-rides-waterslides&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196770/planet-coaster-2-water-park-rides-waterslides" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196770/planet-coaster-2-water-park-rides-waterslides</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-11T17:52:15-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-11T17:52:15-04:00</updated><title>现在最值得购买的电子书阅读器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;蓝色背景下空中漂浮的各种物体&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ahl9GA-W3_l8GrBRn3vh1DQwhUU=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox- cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72396035/236754_Best_ebook_readers_for_2023_WJoel.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Will Joel / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;从在浴缸里读书到在浴缸里乱写乱画从深入亚马逊生态系统到彻底避开它，每个人都有一款电子阅读器。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23769068/best-ebook-读者&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23769068/best-ebook-readers" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23769068/best-ebook-readers</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-11T17:29:59-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-11T17:29:59-04:00</updated><title> Google Pixel 9：迄今为止的所有泄密和谣言</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Pixel 9、9 Pro 和 9 Pro XL 并排的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/DpeqXCNg9I8vam-SF_Iu8jCS_ZY=/150x0:1770x1080/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73456101/pixel9fam.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;泄露的 Pixel 9、9 Pro 和 9 Pro XL。&lt;/em>; |图片来源：Rozetked&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;Pixel 再次泄露，这一次，看起来更大的 Pixel 9 Pro &#39;XL&#39; 即将在 8 月推出，而且速度很快。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt; a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24196571/google-pixel-9-pro-xl-9a-fold-rumors-leaks-camera&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24196571/google-pixel-9-pro-xl-9a-fold-rumors-leaks-camera" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24196571/google-pixel-9-pro-xl-9a-fold-rumors-leaks-camera</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name><name>艾玛·罗斯</name><name>理查德·劳勒</name><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-11T16:06:15-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-11T16:06:15-04:00</updated><title>苹果 AirPods Max 首次跌破 400 美元</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Apple AirPods Max 耳机的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/43L5AEhWIJUg476cTvNzM7XvpwY=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73455932/DSCF2505_Enhanced_NR.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;对于大音质而言，价格偏高，但 AirPods Max 的价格更合理，为 398 美元。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Chris Welch / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;7ZG1WA&quot;>;Apple 第一代产品的高端定价始终让我惊叹不已 — 只需看看 &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/24054862/apple-vision-pro-review-vr-ar-headset-features-price&quot;>;3,500 美元 Apple Vision Pro&lt;/a>; 或其 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/2020/3/2/21161487/apple-mac-pro-display-xdr-review-6k-lcd-screen-price-features&quot;>;5,000 美元的显示屏&lt;/a>;。 AirPods Max 的售价也可能比其应有的 549 美元贵一些，但与苹果豪华降噪耳机的竞争对手相比，这个价格相对温和。值得庆幸的是，现在精选颜色的产品降价至 398 美元（折扣 151 美元）&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/New-Apple-AirPods-Max-Space/dp/B08PZHYWJS/?tag=theverge02 -20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;亚马逊&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://goto.walmart.com/c/482924/565706/9383?u=https%3A %2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FApple-AirPods-Max-Space-Gray%2F774269130&amp;amp;sharedid=theverge.com&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;沃尔玛&lt;/a>;，这是创历史新低。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;VhPP0B&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;productcard:12040633&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;HxESTS&quot;>;有些人可能会觉得自从&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22177494/apple-airpods-max-headphones-review-price-features&quot;>;我们在 2020 年首次评测以来，AirPods Max 已经有些年头了&lt; /a>;，但苹果的无线耳机仍然是我们向苹果用户推荐的首选，也是一些&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21345733/best-noise-canceling-headphones&quot;>;最好的耳机&lt;/ a>;总体而言。它们听起来几乎和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23067645/sony-wh-1000xm5-noise-canceling-headphones-review&quot;>;索尼...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p一样好>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196451/apple-airpods-max-noise-canceling-headphones-deal-sale&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a >; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196451/apple-airpods-max-noise-canceling-headphones-deal-sale" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196451/apple-airpods-max-noise-canceling-headphones-deal-sale</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-11T15:56:17-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-11T15:56:17-04:00</updated><title>传统基金会坚称它没有被“同性恋毛茸茸”黑客攻击</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;透明笔记本电脑在监视墙前的艺术渲染。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/3Loq91JL87qbOB823g88hTs0QOc=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73455899/akrales_220309_4977_0292 .0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;APqr5P&quot;>;一群自称“毛茸茸的同性恋黑客”这样说 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www .theverge.com/2024/7/9/24195341/hacktivists-release-heritage-foundation-data-allegedly-stolen-in-response-to-project-2025&quot;>;本月早些时候违反了传统基金会&lt;/a>;，释放 2 GB 的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://theintercept.com/2024/07/09/gay-furry-hackers-claim-credit-for-hacking-heritage-foundation-over-project-2025/&quot;>;周二右翼智库的内部数据&lt;/a>;。黑客行动组织 SiegedSec 在其 Telegram 频道上表示，该组织此前曾声称对&lt;a href=&quot;https://cyberscoop.com/nato-siegedsec-breac/&quot;>;黑客攻击北约计算机系统&lt;/a>;负责，该组织表示，Heritage 黑客事件是 #OpTransRights 活动的一部分，该活动还针对极右媒体渠道 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.dailydot.com/debug/furry-hackers-siegedsec-real-americas-voice/&quot;>;Real America&#39;s之声&lt;/a>;和新颂大型教堂。该组织还指出，他们对“2025 计划”（传统基金会为前总统唐纳德·特朗普连任提出的政策建议）的反对是一个激励因素。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;u6tjd7&quot;>;在给 &lt;em>;The 的电子邮件中Verge&lt;/em>;，传统基金会发言人诺亚·温里希...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196554/siegedsec-heritage-foundation- project-2025-hack-gay-furry&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196554/siegedsec-heritage-foundation-project-2025-hack-gay-furry" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196554/siegedsec-heritage-foundation-project-2025-hack-gay-furry</id><author><name>盖比·德尔·瓦莱</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-11T15:31:26-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-11T15:31:26-04:00</updated><title> Arm 宣布推出一款适用于手机的开源图形升级器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;粉红色背景上显示 Arm 徽标的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/rl9p7ll1JvQA9XUcVplsUs6xxvo=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn .com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73455828/acastro_STK053_02.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Alex Castro / The Verge 的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;UJIP5w&quot;>;Arm 正在推出自己的产品移动游戏升级器。芯片设计师&lt;a href=&quot;https://community.arm.com/arm-community-blogs/b/graphics-gaming-and-vr-blog/posts/introducing-arm-accuracy-super-resolution&quot;>;说其 Arm 精度超分辨率&lt;/a>; (ASR) 可以让游戏看起来更好，同时降低手机的功耗。它还根据 MIT 开源许可证向开发人员提供升级技术。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;gdz2A3&quot;>;Arm 的技术基于 AMD 的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/ 2022/3/23/22993152/amd-fsr-2-0-xbox-nvidia-gpus&quot;>;FidelityFX 超分辨率 2 (FSR 2)&lt;/a>;，它使用时间升级来使 PC 游戏看起来更好并提高帧速率。与基于单帧放大图像的空间放大不同，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.tomshardware.com/news/amd-universal-upscaling-radeon-super-resolution-fsr-2#:~:文本=空间%20upscaling%20意味着%20the%20only%20data%20used%20for%20upscaling%20a%20frame%20来自%20the%20frame%20本身。%20Temporal%20upscaling%20in%20contrast%20can%20use%20data%20from %20the%20current%20frame%20as%20well%20as%20previous%20frames。&quot;>;时间升级涉及&lt;/a>;使用多个帧来生成更高质量的图像。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;rlnCoB&quot;>;升级对于无法以可玩帧速率运行游戏的低功耗显卡特别有用。 AMD FSR，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/8/22/23841148/nvidia-dlss-3-5-ray-reconstruction-ray-tracing-quality&quot;>;Nvidia...&lt; /a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196566/arm-asr-game-upscaler-for-mobile-devices&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip ;&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196566/arm-asr-game-upscaler-for-mobile-devices" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/7/11/24196566/arm-asr-game-upscaler-for-mobile-devices</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-07-11T14:37:18-04:00</published><updated> 2024-07-11T14:37:18-04:00</updated><title>麦克斯毕竟可能不是值得一看的人</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;HBO Max 徽标的插图，上面潦草地写着“HBO”。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/SZQs91bJDPoxPnQfUrHApX7M52E=/0x1:2040x1361/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73455603/acastro_STK055_03_max.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;u15ca1&quot;>;过去几年，华纳兄弟探索频道 (Warner Bros. Discovery) 一直在 Max 上推出其基于 IP 的新剧集 &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2023/4/12/23677909/hbo-discovery-combined-max-streaming-service-price-availability&quot;>;努力